[A Dream Within A Dream]

2
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:57,850
[Episode 17]

3
00:02:03,070 --> 00:02:03,920
What is it?

4
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,850
What's going on?

5
00:02:06,310 --> 00:02:08,960
I heard your Chief Master's called
something like "Liu"?

6
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,800
I'm known as "Thriver" on the streets,

7
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,960
specializing in dealing with these famous
troublemakers in the martial world.

8
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:14,900
Hurry up

9
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,880
and tell him to come out to see me!

10
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,190
Boss.

11
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,640
This woman is so pretty.

12
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:30,960
Miss.

13
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,680
Do I look like your future husband?

14
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:34,820
More like a fly.

15
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:36,520
Miss.

16
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,000
So beautiful.

17
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,000
Boss!

18
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:43,870
Boss!

19
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:45,210
Are you okay, Boss?

20
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,430
Capture that woman!

21
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,120
Yes!

22
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:49,960
Stop!

23
00:02:52,260 --> 00:02:54,590
Phantom dragon lurks in the black market.

24
00:02:54,650 --> 00:02:57,380
Radiant lanterns
illuminate the Nightwalkers.

25
00:02:59,940 --> 00:03:02,660
♪ Phantom dragon
lurks in the black market ♪

26
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:07,540
♪ Radiant lanterns
illuminate the Nightwalkers ♪

27
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:08,800
It's the Moon Immortal.

28
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,260
♪ In the dark of night,
pure dreams run deep and wide ♪

29
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,890
♪ Who dares to join the game?
This isn't child's play ♪

30
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,800
Shangguan.

31
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,750
The flute.

32
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:29,390
Are you the one who's called something
like "Liu?"

33
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:30,960
On the streets, I go by the name...

34
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,840
Sir,

35
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:33,840
you ruined our stage.

36
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:35,520
The fine is

37
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:37,280
200 taels of silver.

38
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,000
On the streets, I go by the name...

39
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,840
Miss,

40
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,280
you broke our wine jar.

41
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:43,250
The fine is 50 taels of silver.

42
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,560
But this gentleman

43
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,960
disturbed this young lady,

44
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,240
which was truly uncalled for.

45
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,430
In my opinion,

46
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,140
the fine for the young lady

47
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:53,280
should be put on this gentleman's tab.

48
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,079
Please pay.

49
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,280
On the streets, I go by the name...

50
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,480
Master Thief Shanhu.

51
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,820
It seems this crappy ax

52
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,130
is worth some pennies.

53
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:05,240
How about

54
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:07,330
giving it to the young lady

55
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,860
to calm her nerves?

56
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,160
Look.

57
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:21,310
Your ax has disturbed this
young lady again.

58
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:22,840
Kneel and plead guilty now.

59
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,430
You bastard "Liu" something...

60
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:26,360
Speedy Yunlong.

61
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,190
Even your boss is already on his knees.

62
00:04:34,190 --> 00:04:35,590
What are you waiting for?

63
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,720
Peonies?

64
00:04:46,090 --> 00:04:47,330
Tacky.

65
00:04:47,630 --> 00:04:48,630
Lotuses?

66
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:50,630
Mediocre.

67
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,240
Roses?

68
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,070
Dull.

69
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,600
A fine sword suits a
noble gentleman;

70
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,720
and jade bamboo is a gift for
a beautiful lady.

71
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,680
Miss, may I ask

72
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,590
your gracious name?

73
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,330
No need for honorifics.

74
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:15,680
I live in the west of the city

75
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,430
outside the Shiqiao Gate, at the Duke of
Guangping's Residence,

76
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:19,630
who's Left Vice Minister of the Imperial Secretariat
and concurrently Minister of War.

77
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:21,040
My name is Song Yiting.

78
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,400
Chu Guihong.

79
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,970
Since you had the guts to shoot him,

80
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,560
how come you don't have the guts
to clean up the mess?

81
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,680
And you come here now, expecting me

82
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,280
to clean up this mess for you?

83
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:40,240
Well...

84
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,040
Father.

85
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,800
You know,

86
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,630
with Heng's skills,

87
00:05:42,630 --> 00:05:44,270
there's no way he would've failed to
dodge that arrow.

88
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,510
He must have done it on purpose.

89
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:47,870
He... He had long planned to kick Guihong
out of the capital.

90
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:49,480
Don't you fall into his trap.

91
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,240
Shut up!

92
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,380
You useless thing.

93
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,620
Your Majesty.

94
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,190
I am to blame for what happened
at the stables.

95
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:01,160
But the Seventh Prince

96
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,800
networks with top officials at court,

97
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,510
forges alliances with underworld
forces outside the court,

98
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:06,430
has control over the major force of
the Xuanjia Army,

99
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:07,800
and even seeks to strengthen his power

100
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,800
through a marriage alliance
with the Song family.

101
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:12,510
Such treacherous ambitions are
blatantly obvious.

102
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:14,910
Please make a wise decision, Your Majesty.

103
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,280
Your Majesty.

104
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,310
Your Majesty!

105
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:26,950
Your Majesty.

106
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:30,410
Chancellor Gao and the others have
arrived at the palace gate.

107
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:32,360
Are they trying to stage a coup?

108
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,970
What do you gentlemen intend to do?

109
00:06:38,970 --> 00:06:40,930
Don't stir up trouble here!

110
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,440
If you anger His Majesty,

111
00:06:42,460 --> 00:06:44,460
I'm afraid you'll face punishment!

112
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,159
Chu Guihong shot the prince,

113
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,390
which is unforgivable.

114
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:52,600
I, Yao Qian,

115
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,970
beg Your Majesty to judge wisely.

116
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:57,760
Your Majesty, please judge wisely!

117
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,430
If you keep sighing like that,

118
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:15,230
you might just sigh my soul away.

119
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,390
Help me up.

120
00:07:33,670 --> 00:07:35,020
Be gentler, okay?

121
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,240
Your Highness,

122
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,659
what a smart tactic.

123
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:42,600
You used me to irritate Chu Guihong again.

124
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,800
Now His Majesty is furious in the palace,

125
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,750
and you've made a stir
in the entire court.

126
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:49,280
Don't you think you've gone too far
this time?

127
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:51,750
Didn't you say my tactic was
old-fashioned?

128
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:53,040
As long as it works, right?

129
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,830
You...

130
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,920
Only someone like you

131
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,270
would come up with a move that
does even more harm

132
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,930
to yourself than to the enemy.

133
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,630
If I didn't risked myself

134
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,070
to make Chu Guihong commit
a grave mistake,

135
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:08,390
how could you break off the
engagement with him?

136
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:09,560
And I'm telling you,

137
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,390
when they come in a while,

138
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:12,800
be clear in your mind about

139
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,190
what's safe to say and what's not.

140
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,950
We are on the same boat.

141
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,390
I'm telling you too.

142
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,920
Breaking off the engagement

143
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,000
and marrying you

144
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,400
are two separate things.

145
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,430
You're the God of Death.

146
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:30,530
You must keep your word.

147
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,600
Don't try to play dirty, you hear me?

148
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,289
Do you hear me?

149
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:35,200
It hurts.

150
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,030
Do you hear me?

151
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:42,150
Who's the one playing dirty?

152
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,120
Your Highness, now you know
what pain feels like?

153
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,200
Then why didn't you dodge

154
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,330
that arrow just now?

155
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,240
I...

156
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:51,960
His Majesty is here.

157
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:58,010
Your Highness.

158
00:08:58,150 --> 00:08:59,790
Your Highness, are you alright?

159
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:01,590
Why are you bleeding so much?

160
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,630
Hang in there.

161
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:04,960
The imperial physician will be here
in no time.

162
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,750
My Lady.

163
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:07,960
Mother.

164
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,440
Why are you bleeding so much again?

165
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,750
I-It was her.

166
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:11,790
Just now, she...

167
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:12,440
My Lady.

168
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:14,240
It's all my fault.

169
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:15,790
Sorry for making you worry.

170
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:16,670
Good girl.

171
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:18,350
You're just too concerned.

172
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,200
Heng, come on.

173
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,030
Be careful, Your Highness.

174
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:35,790
Slowly.

175
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:38,870
Be careful.

176
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:39,790
Slowly.

177
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:51,250
Greetings, Your Majesty.

178
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,200
Song.

179
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,390
You rise first.

180
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,040
Thank you, Your Majesty.

181
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,750
You!

182
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:17,360
Answer me.

183
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:19,840
Yes.

184
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,250
Your Majesty.

185
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,810
Heng is severely injured.

186
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,020
Might he rise first and answer you?

187
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,550
Your uncle is inciting officials outside
the palace gate

188
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:29,330
to stage a coup.

189
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,510
What,

190
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:33,160
are you trying to defy me here as well?

191
00:10:33,290 --> 00:10:34,210
I dare not.

192
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:51,280
How do you intend to punish Chu Guihong?

193
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:53,960
Your Majesty.

194
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,960
Your Highness...

195
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:04,790
Chu Guihong is the capital prefect

196
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:08,060
and the only surviving child
of Lord Qianyu.

197
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:10,280
He's also a great talent to our nation.

198
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,930
If he's to be punished,

199
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:15,600
I believe all the officials will
be disappointed as well.

200
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,600
But according to the law of Great Jing,

201
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,800
Article 8 states that

202
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:21,260
plotting to harm a member
of the royal family...

203
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,840
Plotting to harm a member
of the royal family

204
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,440
shall be regarded as treason

205
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:30,550
and shall be executed
according to the law.

206
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:32,350
So, Your Majesty, I'm just as

207
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,600
conflicted as you are.

208
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:49,790
Being so seriously injured,

209
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:51,510
yet you're still concerned about

210
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:52,670
my difficulties.

211
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,720
Heng, you do put the bigger picture first.

212
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:05,150
But I see your arrow wound

213
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:09,000
is about an inch above the left
side of your chest.

214
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:11,920
I suppose it's not very serious, is it?

215
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,810
Thank you for your concern, Your Majesty.

216
00:12:16,290 --> 00:12:17,690
But if Your Majesty would

217
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,000
graciously revoke the decree

218
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,400
and annul the engagement

219
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:23,280
between Miss Song and Chu Guihong,

220
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,330
then the knot in my heart

221
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:27,160
would be untied,

222
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,220
and I believe my wounds

223
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:30,840
would heal faster.

224
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,870
So about what happened at the
stables today...

225
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:36,270
I was just fooling around

226
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:38,710
with Chu Guihong at the stables.

227
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,360
We were merely fooling around,

228
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,790
so a few bumps were inevitable.

229
00:12:41,790 --> 00:12:43,050
It's nothing serious.

230
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,720
Since it's a simple misunderstanding,

231
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,450
this should be easy to resolve.

232
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,060
Song.

233
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,030
Tell me,

234
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:58,840
do you have feelings for General Chu?

235
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:00,440
Your Majesty,

236
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:02,440
I have absolutely no improper thoughts
toward him.

237
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,240
Alright.

238
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,960
Though the imperial edict for
your betrothal

239
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,830
was issued 18 years ago,

240
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,270
since there's no affection

241
00:13:09,270 --> 00:13:10,840
between you two now,

242
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:11,910
I

243
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:15,440
have no wish to add yet another pair
of ill-fated couple to the world.

244
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,790
I hereby declare that

245
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,200
this betrothal is annulled.

246
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,240
However,

247
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:29,230
Song is not young anymore,

248
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:31,480
and Song Yude is already aged.

249
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:33,200
He has long hoped to see
his children married

250
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,510
and live out his remaining days in peace.

251
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:35,750
His wishes align closely

252
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:38,000
with mine.

253
00:13:38,510 --> 00:13:40,360
Although this betrothal has been
cancelled,

254
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,030
it must be

255
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:43,440
made up for with another.

256
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:44,790
Liu Mingxi.

257
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,160
Your Majesty.

258
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,310
Bring my jade seal.

259
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:49,630
Today,

260
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,840
in front of the Noble Consort,

261
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:55,030
I'll betroth Song as Heng's
principal consort.

262
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,630
Your Majesty, that's not right.

263
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:59,200
This is supposed to be just a broken
betrothal, Your Majesty.

264
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,030
Thank you for granting our marriage,
Your Majesty.

265
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:01,840
I...

266
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,160
By the way,

267
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:09,440
there was an old custom
in the previous dynasty

268
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:11,910
that once a prince gets married,
he must go and govern his fief.

269
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:13,790
Now that you've been bestowed
a principal consort,

270
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:15,270
once you recover from your injury,

271
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:16,120
you shall set out

272
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,600
for your fief.

273
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:20,870
Your Maj...

274
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,610
Since you're here,

275
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,400
come have a drink with me.

276
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,810
I never expected

277
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:05,840
this place

278
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:07,960
to be so complicated.

279
00:16:09,390 --> 00:16:11,250
The good people I once believed in

280
00:16:12,270 --> 00:16:13,300
might not

281
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,730
be so good after all.

282
00:16:16,630 --> 00:16:19,120
And the ones I thought were bad

283
00:16:19,910 --> 00:16:21,090
might

284
