You mean

287
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:30,500
you came from somewhere else?

288
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:36,200
But who's not?

289
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,460
We are all visitors here,

290
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:42,200
unable to escape from this worldly cage.

291
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,230
Everyone

292
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,800
have responsibilities they can't
walk away from.

293
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,570
You're like this,

294
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:50,270
so am I,

295
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,550
and so is everyone.

296
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,190
I never noticed before

297
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:59,080
that as the second female lead,

298
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:01,140
you're actually quite open-minded.

299
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:03,080
The second female lead?

300
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:06,369
It doesn't matter.

301
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,599
What matters is

302
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:10,310
you're more persistent than me.

303
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:11,400
You said you wouldn't get married,

304
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,599
