307
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,000
No.

308
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:21,880
Not at all.

309
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,359
I think it's a good thing.

310
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:25,240
You should always hold on to

311
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:26,920
everything you desire.

312
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:29,440
Don't ever let worldly norms,

313
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,680
responsibilities,

314
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,450
or royal orders weigh you down.

315
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,060
Since you've thought it all through,

316
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,350
why are you still here

317
00:17:37,350 --> 00:17:39,350
