The one I like doesn't like me back,

320
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:55,200
the one I don't like was injured by me,

321
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:58,960
and there's another one who I want to
run away from but can't

322
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:01,030
because we're bound by fate.

323
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:03,930
I understand.

324
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,040
In the past,

325
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:08,200
