330
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:22,640
Be...

331
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:24,000
Be...

332
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,200
Nan Heng?

333
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:26,550
Of course not.

334
00:18:29,570 --> 00:18:30,980
That's good.

335
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:32,370
You scared me.

336
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:34,540
Remember, Song Yiting.

337
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,400
Once you get involved with Nan Heng,

338
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:38,070
