especially not

342
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,410
by the water,

343
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,400
in private rooms,

344
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:45,270
or during any assassination attempts.

345
00:18:45,270 --> 00:18:46,030
Never.

346
00:18:46,270 --> 00:18:47,240
Do you hear me?

347
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:51,000
Aren't these exactly the things

348
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,000
