Instead of worrying about me,

355
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:04,000
you should worry more about yourself.

356
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:04,830
At least,

357
00:19:04,980 --> 00:19:06,590
I know how I feel.

358
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:07,650
But what about you?

359
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:09,000
Do you really know

360
00:19:09,310 --> 00:19:10,720
