362
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,880
Of course I do.

363
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:18,900
I like...

364
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,440
I like...

365
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:23,800
You like Father and Mother,

366
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:25,310
you like Zhixia and Yingqiu,

367
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:26,170
and you like me.

368
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,440
You seem to like everyone,

369
00:19:28,590 --> 00:19:29,920
but it actually shows that

370
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:31,180
