Sometimes,

372
00:19:33,890 --> 00:19:35,890
I think you're a bit weird.

373
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:39,070
You seem to be happy around everyone,

374
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,550
but you've never really

375
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:43,190
had feelings for anyone,

376
