00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:19,230
Whoever is willing to hand over
10,000 soldiers

842
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:21,000
to guard the border in Dongshuo,

843
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,790
I will grant their request.

844
00:39:30,590 --> 00:39:31,480
Your Majesty.

845
00:39:31,510 --> 00:39:32,640
This cannot be done.

846
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:35,070
The Seventh Prince and Mr. Chu

847
00:39:35,110 --> 00:39:36,910
are both pillars of our country.

848
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:39,710
How can they be punished because of me?

849
00:39:39,710 --> 00:39:41,840
I want to hear it from them personally!

850
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:44,440
What?

851
00:39:45,280 --> 00:39:46,810
Why are you both silent now?

852
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:50,140
Don't you both want to marry Song Yimeng?

853
00:39:50,380 --> 00:39:52,400
Aren't you both willing to suffer

854
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:54,320
physical pain for a woman?

855
00:39:55,030 --> 00:39:57,230
As soon as you heard about
giving up military power,

856
00:39:57,230 --> 00:39:58,590
you both went quiet.

857
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,230
Lost your voices?

858
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:03,330
Guihong, are you crazy?

859
00:40:03,510 --> 00:40:04,320
Father!

860
00:40:05,070 --> 00:40:06,180
How about

861
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:07,800
I take the punishment for Mr. Song?

862
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:08,960
Get lost.

863
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:10,710
I... I...

864
00:40:10,710 --> 00:40:11,510
Your Majesty.

865
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:13,400
I'm willing to bear the punishment
in place of Mr. Song.

866
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:14,030
Good.

867
00:40:14,030 --> 00:40:14,830
Your Majesty.

868
00:40:17,070 --> 00:40:17,990
However,

869
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:20,300
your 10,000 Xuanjia Army soldiers

870
00:40:20,300 --> 00:40:22,690
will never return to your command again.

871
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:24,920
Heng.

872
00:40:26,230 --> 00:40:28,000
You'd better think it through.

873
00:40:31,510 --> 00:40:32,630
I have.

874
00:40:33,710 --> 00:40:34,710
Song Yimeng

875
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:37,630
is the principal consort I
worked so hard to secure,

876
00:40:37,630 --> 00:40:38,760
which makes Mr. Song

877
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:40,030
my father-in-law.

878
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:42,230
It's only natural to bear the punishment

879
00:40:42,230 --> 00:40:43,490
for my father-in-law.

880
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:47,000
In that case,

881
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:49,710
I'll grant your wish.

882
00:40:54,140 --> 00:40:55,080
Eunuch Liu.

883
00:40:56,030 --> 00:40:57,000
Carry out the punishment.
